  <title>
    <phrase lang="en">Guides</phrase>
    <phrase lang="de">Hilfslinie</phrase>
    <phrase lang="fr">Guides</phrase>
    <phrase lang="no">Hjelpelinjer</phrase>
  </title>
  
  <indexterm lang="en"><primary>Guides</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="de"><primary>Hilfslinie</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="fr"><primary>Guides</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="no">
    <primary>Bilete (menyen)</primary>
    <secondary>Hjelpelinjer</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="no"><primary>Hjelpelinjer</primary></indexterm>
  

  <figure>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">
        The <quote>Guides</quote> options of the <quote>Image</quote>
        submenu
      </phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Das Untermenü <quote>Hilfslinie</quote></phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Les options Guides du sous-menu Image</phrase>
      <phrase lang="no">
        Undermenyen <quote>Hjelpelinjer</quote> i menyen <quote>Bilete</quote>
      </phrase>
    </title>

    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject lang="en;de">
        <imagedata fileref="../images/menus/image-guides.png" format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject lang="fr">
        <imagedata fileref="../images/menus/fr/image-guides.png" format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject lang="no">
        <imagedata fileref="../images/menus/no/image-guides.png" format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
    </mediaobject>
  </figure>
  
  <para lang="en">
    The <guimenuitem>Guides</guimenuitem> submenu contains various commands
    for the creation and removal of guides.
  </para>
  <para lang="de">
    In diesem Untermenü finden Sie verschiedene Kommandos zum erzeugen und
    entfernen von Hilfslinien.
  </para>
  <para lang="fr">
    Cete commande vous apporte quelques améliorations pratiques pour gérer
    les guides.
  </para>
  <para lang="no">
    Undermenyen <guimenuitem>Hjelpelinjer</guimenuitem> inneheld 
    kommandoar for å lage eller fjerne hjelpelinjer.
  </para>
 

  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activating the Submenü</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace dialogu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Aufruf des Untermenüs</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Activer le Dialogue</phrase>
      <phrase lang="no">Aktivering</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">开启对话框</phrase>
    </title>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          You can access this submenu from the image menubar through
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>I</accel>mage</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>G</accel>uides</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Das Untermenü kann aus dem Bildfenster erreicht werden:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>B</accel>ild</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>H</accel>ilfslinie</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          Vous pouvez y accéder par
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>I</accel>mage</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>G</accel>uides</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          Du har tilgang til denne undermenyen på biletmenyen via
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Bilete</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Hjelpelinjer</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>


  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">
        The Contents of the <quote>Guides</quote> Submenu
      </phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Der Inhalt des Untermenüs</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Entrées du sous-menu Guides</phrase>
      <phrase lang="no">
        Innhaldet i menyen <quote>Hjelpelinjer</quote>
      </phrase> 
    </title>
    
    <para lang="en">
      The <guilabel>Guides</guilabel> submenu contains the 
      following commands:
    </para>
    <para lang="de">
      Im Untermenü <guilabel>Hilfslinie</guilabel> stehen Ihnen folgende
      Kommandos zur Verfügung:
    </para>
    <para lang="fr">
      Dans le sous-menu <guilabel>Guides</guilabel> vous trouverez les 
      commandes suivantes:
    </para>
    <para lang="no">
      Menyen <guilabel>Hjelpelinjer</guilabel> inneheld følgjande
      kommandoar:
    </para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-add">New Guide</link>
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-add">Neue Hilfslinie</link>
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-add">Nouveau guide</link>
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-add">Ny hjelpelinje</link>
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-percent">
            New Guide (by Percent)
          </link>
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-percent">
            Neue Hilfslinie (in Prozent)
          </link>
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-percent">
            Nouveau guide (en pourcentage)
          </link>
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-percent">
             Ny hjelpelinje (i prosent)
           </link> 
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-selection">
            New Guides from Selection
          </link>
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-selection">
            Neue Hilfslinien aus Auswahl
          </link>
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-selection">
            Nouveaux guides (Depuis la sélection)
          </link>
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-selection">
            Nye hjelpelinjer frå markering
          </link>
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-remove">Remove all Guides</link>
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-remove">
            Alle Hilfslinien entfernen
          </link>
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-remove">Enlever les guides</link>
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          <link linkend="gimp-image-guides-remove">
            Fjern alle hjelpelinjer
          </link>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
